quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  75,31,Ariko (umuhakanyi) ntiyigeze yemera ndetse nta n’ubwo yigeze asali
  75,32,Ahubwo yahinyuye (Qur’an) maze ayitera umugongo
  75,33,Hanyuma akagenda yibona yerekeza mu muryango we
  75,34,Ufite akaga (yewe muntu w’umuhakanyi)! Kandi na none ufite akaga
  75,35,Nyamara ufite akaga (yewe muntu w’umuhakanyi)! Kandi ufite akaga
  75,36,Ese umuntu yibwira ko azarekwa gusa (atabajijwe ibyo yakoze ngo abihemberwe cyangwa ngo abihanirwe)
  75,37,Ese ntiyari intanga mu masohoro asohowe
  75,38,"Hanyuma akaba urusoro rw’amaraso, maze Allah akamurema, akanamutunganya (akaba umuntu wuzuye)"
  75,39,"Maze akamuremamo ibitsina bibiri: gabo na gore"
  75,40,Ese uwo (Allah ukora ibyo) si We ushoboye kuzura abapfuye